name: WMIX2023-5000
description:
This model was trained with photos of different woman portraits, so is capable to recreate some races, this model is completely free.

You can put the file in the embeddings folder inside stable diffusion, and reload the model in the textual inversion tab.

Download, share don't forget to give some credit, have fun.

Here is a sample of the prompt I use to avoid loading the Asian faces that is by default:

Masterpiece, Ultra High Definition, 3/4 body shot, photo-portrait of an attractive Afro ((WMIX2023-5000)), see-through lingerie, exquisite modern fashion, elegant standing pose, confident smile, intricate ornaments, highly detailed fashion photography, bright and vibrant colors:0.8, natural light, volumetric lighting, depth of field, (HyperStylizeV6:0.9), (Fujifilm GFX 100: Combine with Fujifilm GF 63mm f/2.8 R WR lens for exceptional medium format image quality. Explore film simulation modes and experiment with creative filters for unique artistic effects), skyscrapers and citys-cape background.
